Text: Reception Honoring Gov Gray DavisJoe Lieberman Congresswoman Jane and Dr Sidney Harman along with the Democratic Governors Association New Democrat Network and the Democratic California Congressional Delegation Invite you to attend a Reception benefiting GOVERNOR GRAY DAVIS of California Hosted by Congresswoman Jane and Dr Sidney Harman with Special Guest Senator Joseph Lieberman July pm Offices of Harman International Pennsylvania Avenue NW The attached Adobe Acrobat file contains the complete invitation and registration form Davispdf
